I have all the girls' names.

846
00:42:21,600 --> 00:42:23,040
What's the name of your girl?

847
00:42:23,040 --> 00:42:23,760
I'll get one for you.

848
00:42:24,360 --> 00:42:25,100
This one, right?

849
00:42:25,100 --> 00:42:26,080
(Shu)

850
