♪Until the end of her life♪

881
00:44:43,255 --> 00:44:46,055
♪When I look back one day♪

882
00:44:46,175 --> 00:44:49,295
♪I'll let go of everything♪

883
00:44:49,615 --> 00:44:55,815
♪I'll hold your hand
and never let you down♪

